<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Title format</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">Enter, '[Description] (Tariff quota notice [number])'.</p>

<p class="govuk-body">For example, 'Agricultural and industrial products (Tariff Quota Notice 151)'.</p>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Collection page</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
Add the document to the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/tariff-quota-notices-2014" class="govuk-link">Tariff quota notices collection</a>. Do not create a public change note.
</p>
